    description:
      'Everything which you have researched so far has finally culminated together to discover the quintessential key to the secrets of the universe.\nThe Shard of Creation: a shard of condensed primal magic which contains age-old energies from a time when the universe was yet to exist. Using this shard as a source of power, you have access to magic which may alter the very fabric of existence.\nAs soon as the infusion was complete, a sensation of pure clarity filled your twisted mind, you had a revelation, it is all clear to you now. You are not a madman.',
